<title>msẖ bʿyd ʿlyk yạrb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 msẖ bʿyd ʿlyk yạrb msẖ bʿyd ạ̉bdạaⁿ ʿlyk
 msẖ bʿyd mạnt ạlmḥb wạmạ nṣrkẖ nltqyk
 wlyk fy ạlmwt bybạn mạysẖwfhạsẖ ạlʿyạn
 wlyk fy bḥwr ạlạmnạ mʿạbr llạ̉mạn
 wlw ạlʿtmẗ tʿạfr tḥṭ llylnạ ạ̉kẖr
 bfjr fyh ạlạ̹jạbẗ wạltʿwyḍ lly ṣạbr
 trd ḥq ạlḍʿạf yrjʿ lhm ạ̉ḍʿạf
 wạlly byḍḥk ạ̉kẖrhạ yḍḥk zạỷd htạf</lyrics>
</song>